<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śākavarṣaṁbulu 990 svasti sarvvalōkāśraya śrīviṣṇuvarddhanamahārājula
<lb n="2"/>pravarddhamāna vijayarājyasaṁvatsarā 8 dina 11 viśakhavaṭṭanamu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>na kammakōmaṭi mēḍiyasseṭṭi koḍuku pāpaya tulāmāsamuna
<lb n="4"/>kṛṣṇapakṣamuna trayōdaśi śrībhīmēsvaramahādēvarakuṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍa
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vartti lōhadiviya 1 dīniki nācaṁdrarkkamuṁ neyi sariyiṁppaṁggalavā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rugā śrībhīmēsvaramahādēvara kilaramuna cāmiyabōyu vaṁṭiya
<lb n="7" break="no"/>yu badiyabhōyu doḍḍiyayu komma<unclear>bhō</unclear>la peddiyayu kommabōla talli
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yayu berasina bōla vasamunaṁ beṭṭina Eḍlu 50 divasapaḍi vōyaṁga
<lb n="9" break="no"/>la tribhuvanāṁkuśamuna nē māna 1 likhitaṁ peddanācāryyaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

